Kubernetes Deployment:
‚óè Deploy the services given in the above-mentioned repository to a local
Kubernetes cluster (e.g., Minikube or Kind).

1.Deploying to miniKube using following commands

kubectl apply -f backend-deployment.yaml
kubectl apply -f frontend-deployment.yaml

2.Get Minikube ip   

minikube ip

3.open the browser
Open `http://<minikube-ip>:30000` in your browser.

4.  Runthe test

pytest tests .py


